@section rd_multiprotocol_support_new Adding a new Radio Arbiter

To add a new Radio Arbiter, implement all functions defined in the `/src/raal/nrf_raal_api.h` file.
A new define, for example, RAAL_NEW_ARBITER, should also be introduced to make the compilation process easier.

